@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
# Para `dotnet run` local use: @baseUrl = http://localhost:5206
# Reemplace {{documentId}} por el id devuelto al registrar un documento.
@documentId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Listar documentos (los sembrados aparecen aquí)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents
Accept: application/json

### Listar por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents?status=Rejected
Accept: application/json

### Registrar documento con su primera versión (multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary

--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

Contrato Demo HTTP
--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Type"

Contract
--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="UploadedBy"

juan.author
--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="contrato-v1.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../../samples/contrato-v1.pdf
--Boundary--

### Detalle del documento con historial de versiones
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}
Accept: application/json

### Enviar a revisión (Created -> PendingReview)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "PendingReview", "performedBy": "juan.author" }

### Tomar la revisión (PendingReview -> UnderReview)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "UnderReview", "performedBy": "maria.reviewer" }

### Registrar una observación
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/observations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CorrectionRequest",
  "content": "El plazo de la cláusula 2 no coincide con lo cotizado.",
  "createdBy": "maria.reviewer"
}

### Rechazar con motivo (UnderReview -> Rejected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetStatus": "Rejected",
  "performedBy": "maria.reviewer",
  "reason": "Corregir plazo y precio antes de reenviar."
}

### Subir versión corregida (Rejected -> PendingReview automático)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/versions
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary

--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="UploadedBy"

juan.author
--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="contrato-v2.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../../samples/contrato-v2.pdf
--Boundary--

### Aprobar (primero volver a UnderReview, luego Approved)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "Approved", "performedBy": "maria.reviewer" }

### Observaciones del documento
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/observations
Accept: application/json

### Trazabilidad completa (auditoría)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/history
Accept: application/json

### Descargar el PDF vigente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/file

### Descargar la versión 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/versions/1/file
